<li><a href="http://www.aolatschool.com/students/math" class="external text" title="http://www.aolatschool.com/students/math" rel="nofollow">K-12 Online Math Resources</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.asiaing.com/examining-gaps-in-mathematics-achievement-among-racial-ethnic-groups-1972.html" class="external text" title="http://www.asiaing.com/examining-gaps-in-mathematics-achievement-among-racial-ethnic-groups-1972.html" rel="nofollow">Examining Gaps in Mathematics Achievement Among Racial-Ethnic Groups, 1972-1992</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.csun.edu/~vcmth00m/bshm.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.csun.edu/~vcmth00m/bshm.html" rel="nofollow">[3]</a> A quarter century of US 'maths wars' and political partisanship. David Klein. California State University, Northridge, USA</li>
<li><a href="http://mathdl.maa.org/convergence/1/?pa=content&amp;sa=viewDocument&amp;nodeId=477&amp;bodyId=595" class="external text" title="http://mathdl.maa.org/convergence/1/?pa=content&amp;sa=viewDocument&amp;nodeId=477&amp;bodyId=595" rel="nofollow">Teaching Leonardo: An Integrated Approach</a> at <a href="http://mathdl.maa.org/convergence/1/" class="external text" title="http://mathdl.maa.org/convergence/1/" rel="nofollow">Convergence</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.adaptivecurriculum.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.adaptivecurriculum.com/" rel="nofollow">Online Math Activity Objects</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mathmotivation.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.mathmotivation.com/" rel="nofollow">Motivational Resources Showing Valuable Applications of Math</a></li>
<li><a href="http://hk.geocities.com/mathphyweb/puremath.htm" class="external text" title="http://hk.geocities.com/mathphyweb/puremath.htm" rel="nofollow">How to Become a Pure Mathematician</a> a List of Undergraduate and Basic Graduate Textbook.</li>
<li><a href="http://mathsolympiad.googlepages.com/ebooks" class="external text" title="http://mathsolympiad.googlepages.com/ebooks" rel="nofollow">Mathematics Related E-books</a></li>
<li><a href="http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/Hbase/hmat.html" class="external text" title="http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/Hbase/hmat.html" rel="nofollow">HyperMath site at Georgia State University</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Teacher_organizations_and_others_associated_with_mathematics_education" id="Teacher_organizations_and_others_associated_with_mathematics_education"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mathematics_education&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Teacher organizations and others associated with mathematics education">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Teacher organizations and others associated with mathematics education</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.nctm.org" class="external text" title="http://www.nctm.org" rel="nofollow">National Council of Teachers of Mathematics</a> (<a href="/wiki/NCTM" title="NCTM" class="mw-redirect">NCTM</a> (USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncetm.org.uk" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.ncetm.org.uk" rel="nofollow">[4]</a> The <a href="/wiki/National_Centre_for_Excellence_in_Teaching_Mathematics" title="National Centre for Excellence in Teaching Mathematics">National Centre for Excellence in Teaching Mathematics</a> (NCETM) (England)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.atm.org.uk" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.atm.org.uk" rel="nofollow">[5]</a> <a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Association_of_Teachers_of_Mathematics&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Association of Teachers of Mathematics (page does not exist)">The Association of Teachers of Mathematics</a> (UK)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ma.org.uk" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.ma.org.uk" rel="nofollow">[6]</a> <a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Mathematical_Association&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Mathematical Association (page does not exist)">The Mathematical Association</a> (UK)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mathemagic.org" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.mathemagic.org" rel="nofollow">[7]</a> <a href="/w/index.php?title=MatheMagic&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="MatheMagic (page does not exist)">MatheMagic</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.snm.org.pl" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.snm.org.pl" rel="nofollow">[8]</a> <a href="/wiki/SNM" title="SNM">SNM</a> (Poland)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.apm.org.po" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.apm.org.po" rel="nofollow">[9]</a> <a href="/wiki/APM" title="APM">APM</a> (Portugal)</li>
<li><a href="http://web.gnowledge.org/mathedu" class="external autonumber" title="http://web.gnowledge.org/mathedu" rel="nofollow">[10]</a> <a href="/wiki/Homi_Bhabha_Centre_for_Science_Education" title="Homi Bhabha Centre for Science Education">Homi Bhabha Centre for Science Education</a> (India)</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Scholarly_journals:_print" id="Scholarly_journals:_print"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mathematics_education&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Scholarly journals: print">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Scholarly journals: print</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://springerlink.metapress.com/app/home/journal.asp?wasp=79421927ccf647fcb830fafe34a31b4a&amp;referrer=parent&amp;backto=linkingpublicationresults,1:102875,1" class="external text" title="http://springerlink.metapress.com/app/home/journal.asp?wasp=79421927ccf647fcb830fafe34a31b4a&amp;referrer=parent&amp;backto=linkingpublicationresults,1:102875,1" rel="nofollow">Educational Studies in Mathematics</a></li>
<li><a href="http://flm.educ.ualberta.ca/" class="external text" title="http://flm.educ.ualberta.ca/" rel="nofollow">For the Learning of Mathematics</a></li>
<li><a href="http://my.nctm.org/eresources/journal_home.asp?journal_id=1" class="external text" title="http://my.nctm.org/eresources/journal_home.asp?journal_id=1" rel="nofollow">Journal for Research in Mathematics Education</a></li>
<li><a href="http://springerlink.metapress.com/content/1573-1820/" class="external text" title="http://springerlink.metapress.com/content/1573-1820/" rel="nofollow">Journal of Mathematics Teacher Education</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.infoagepub.com/products/journals/TMME/" class="external text" title="http://www.infoagepub.com/products/journals/TMME/" rel="nofollow">The Montana Mathematics Enthusiast</a></li>
</ul>
